Interface ModuleIOStream

All Superinterfaces:
ModuleInputStream, ModuleOutputStream, ModuleStream
All Known Implementing Classes:
Captor.IOStream, Container.IOStream, Conveyor.IOStream, Dropper.IOStream, JsonModule.IOStream, Pusher.IOStream
public interface ModuleIOStream
extends ModuleInputStream, ModuleOutputStream
Just allows to create IO stream.

Only the methods ModuleInputStream.write(String) and ModuleOutputStream.read(String) need to be implemented cause the others methods call them
